{"tid":2225488,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美助台升級潛艇 應對解放軍","createTime":"2020-10-01T11:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T11:09:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9ccd040763e1488b04d909fc6852b7feff7e28","tid":2225488,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201001/36RIAXSX5JDCRN6USXOP3QJ2RA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201001%2F36RIAXSX5JDCRN6USXOP3QJ2RA%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w16Fdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=be4a09f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201001%2F36RIAXSX5JDCRN6USXOP3QJ2RA%2F&h=aa442dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201001/36RIAXSX5JDCRN6USXOP3QJ2RA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美助台升級潛艇 應對解放軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q9FYQ9sM4Pgi_98u6ts4JGp__GI=/640x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YO6EQQNW6ZBPFPLYXNXP3BNVRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq9FYQ9sM4Pgi_98u6ts4JGp__GI%3D%2F640x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYO6EQQNW6ZBPFPLYXNXP3BNVRA.jpg&h=28e89ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台軍將為劍龍級潛艇進行升級。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n面對台海緊張局勢，台灣軍方加速發展「不對稱戰力」，國防部進行「劍龍級潛艦戰鬥系統提升案」，由美國協助提升台灣潛艇的系統及技術，美國今年5月已通過知會國會程序。同時，攸關潛艇打擊戰力的MK-48 Mod6 AT長程重型魚雷採購案，台軍規劃首批長程重型魚雷於本年底送抵台灣。<br />\n<br />\n台海軍現役兩艘劍龍級潛艇海龍號及海虎號，。。。。。。。。。。。至於多出的一套系統將會安裝在「潛艇國造」的首艘原型艦中。<br />\n<br />\n潛艇的性能提升後，可強化潛艇的系統處理及運作功能，提高系統穩定度及可靠度，提供早期預警訊息，掌握敵方動態，早先一步執行戰術。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擲14.6億購長程魚雷<br />\n<br />\n同時，為強化潛艇打擊戰力，軍方向美國採購MK-48 Mod6 AT長程型魚雷，包括24枚戰雷丶四枚操雷，總價54.6億新台幣（約14.6億港元），該款重型魚雷最高時速達到55節（時速約101公里），最大續航力50公里，是美國海軍潛艇的主力重型魚雷。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"322ed0fa8bd39d79d29e1330738f0f3f97d60a1d","tid":2225488,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"Taiwan no. 1"},{"pid":"4773d302586b8e13fdede9b82c8f14cb2478e920","tid":2225488,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:09:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}